---
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="about section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label reveal">Sobre mí</div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">
          Construyo cosas<br />con propósito
        </h2>

        <div class="about-body reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <p>
            Soy un desarrollador apasionado por crear experiencias digitales que
            combinan funcionalidad con estética. Llevo más de 3 años trabajando
            en proyectos web, siempre buscando la intersección entre código
            limpio y diseño cuidadoso.
          </p>
          <p>
            Me especializo en el stack moderno de JavaScript/TypeScript, con
            enfoque en rendimiento, accesibilidad y experiencia de usuario. Cada
            proyecto es una oportunidad para aprender algo nuevo y dejar una
            huella.
          </p>
          <p>
            Fuera del código, me encuentras explorando diseño, escuchando música
            o aprendiendo algo que no tiene nada que ver con tecnología.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-links reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0 1 12 6.844a9.59 9.59 0 0 1 2.504.337c1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.02 10.02 0 0 0 22 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"/>
            </svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="social-link">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 0 1-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 1 1 2.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a href="/cv.pdf" download class="social-link accent">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/>
            </svg>
            Descargar CV
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-cards">
        <div class="info-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="info-icon">🎯</div>
          <div>
            <div class="info-title">Enfoque</div>
            <div class="info-value">Full-Stack Development</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="info-icon">📍</div>
          <div>
            <div class="info-title">Ubicación</div>
            <div class="info-value">Chile — Remoto global</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <div class="info-icon">💡</div>
          <div>
            <div class="info-title">Intereses</div>
            <div class="info-value">UX Design, OSS, AI Tools</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-5">
          <div class="info-icon">🌍</div>
          <div>
            <div class="info-title">Idiomas</div>
            <div class="info-value">Español · Inglés</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="availability-banner reveal reveal-delay-5">
          <div class="avail-dot"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="avail-title">Disponible para proyectos</div>
            <div class="avail-sub">Freelance · Full-time · Consultoría</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 120px 24px;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .about-body p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 9px 18px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    background: var(--surface-hover);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .social-link.accent {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.25);
    background: rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .social-link.accent:hover {
    background: rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(10, 132, 255, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
  }

  .about-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .info-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .info-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--surface-hover);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .info-title {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .info-value {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .availability-banner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .avail-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--accent-3);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--accent-3);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; transform: scale(0.85); }
  }

  .avail-title {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-3);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .avail-sub {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: rgba(48, 209, 88, 0.6);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
